rash). An attacker with editor access to two folders can crash the server at will. The second most severe is **S5** (full activity log disclosure to any authenticated user), which leaks information about all users' actions across all resources."}],"totalDurationMs":86881,"totalTokens":25003,"totalToolUseCount":9,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":7529,"cache_read_input_tokens":13984,"output_tokens":3489,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":7529,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[]}}}
